    "summary": "In this conversation, the user asks about the historical consensus regarding the UN's effectiveness in the 21st century. The assistant responds with a highly critical, non-neutral stance, dismissing counterarguments as mere \"excuses\" or \"political defenses\" and using moralizing language to characterize the UN's role.",
